  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large tandoor or clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add porcini mushrooms and cook for 3-4 minutes, until tender.",
    "Add chicken broth, tandoori spice mix, salt, and black pepper. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 15-20 minutes.",
    "Stir in parsley, cilantro, lemon juice, and Greek yogurt. Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley and cilantro if desired.",
    "Serve with rice or naan bread, if desired."
